  <summary date="2019-02-05T20:21:22Z" status="Introduced in House">Human Trafficking Survivor Tax Relief Act 

This bill modifies the requirements for calculating taxable income to exclude from gross income civil damages, restitution, or other monetary awards (including compensatory or statutory damages and restitution imposed in a criminal matter) awarded to victims of peonage, slavery, or human trafficking.</summary>
